# Implement Ledger UI Layer

The goal is to implement the presentation layer for the Ledger feature, allowing users to view balances for all clients and vendors, see transaction details, and add new ledger entries.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The Ledger Homepage will display a single scrollable list of both Clients and Vendors.
> Users can instinctively differentiate them by balance color: Green for Clients and Red for Vendors.
> A filter will be provided to show only Clients, only Vendors, or both.

